overview: The full live-show at De Bosuil (Netherlands), recorded during the "Over Hills And Stones Tour 2012" released November 23, 2012.  Recorded at Muziekcentrum De Bosuil, March 10th 2012, Weert (Netherlands). Live-Mix by Martin „Barni“ Johansson /  Mastered by Kai Stahlenberg (Kohlekeller Studios) / Produced by Cryptex and Special Events Productions.  1. Hicksville, Habitus And Itchy Feet (Live) 03:12  2. Freeride (Live) 02:14  3. Dutch dialogue / Announcement 01:02  4. Dance Of The Strange Folk + Camden Town (Live) 07:25  5. Alois (Live) 03:54  6. It´s Mine (Live) 04:39  7. Gypsy´s Lullaby (Live) 04:15  8. Most Lovable Monster (Live) 05:01  9. Grief And Despair (Live) 05:38  10. Leviathan (Live) 03:21
tagline: Over the Hills and Stones Tour 2012
title: Cryptex: Live at De Bosuil
